Decorations

Goodkit Exclusive

Decoration images with resonsive positioning.

Easily adjust the positioning of the decorations with the responsive positioning and margin utilities. The color of the decorations can be controlled with the .text-{color} utility classes.

<div class="position-absolute text-warning">
  @@include("../partials/decorations/decoration-1.svg")
</div>
<div class="position-absolute text-primary-light">
  @@include("../partials/decorations/decoration-2.svg")
</div>
<div class="position-absolute text-warning">
  @@include("../partials/decorations/decoration-3.svg")
</div>
<div class="position-absolute text-primary">
  @@include("../partials/decorations/decoration-4.svg")
</div>
<div class="position-absolute text-primary">
  @@include("../partials/decorations/decoration-5.svg")
</div>
